<article>
    <h1>LIGHT&#xAD;ING UP FESTIVE SPIRIT WITH KIND ACTS</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20201223/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-12-23"><time>2020-12-23</time></a>
        - <span>THEBIGPICT&#xAD;URE</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>On Christ­mas Day, a spe­cial light show will brighten the fa­cades of The Fuller­ton Ho­tel Sin­ga­pore and the Mer­lion at Ma­rina Bay.</p>
    <p>The show will fea­ture art­works de­pict­ing acts of kind­ness by the com­mu­nity dur­ing the past year.</p>
    <p>Called Share the Mo­ment, the event is one of the key high­lights of Ma­rina Bay Sin­ga­pore Count­down 2021.</p>
    <p>The event also in­cludes an­other pro­jec­tion that starts on Box­ing Day at the ArtS­cience Mu­seum.</p>
    <p>The mu­seum’s fa­cade will be lit up with art­works re­flect­ing hopes and as­pi­ra­tions for Sin­ga­pore.</p>
    <p>The light shows will run ev­ery 15 min­utes from 8pm to 10.30pm un­til New Year’s Eve.</p>
    <p>The shows will be ex­tended to 11.45pm on the fi­nal night.</p>

